title.en: AntV OSCP Doc Season: Hunt Issues to Win Exclusive Merch & Gift Cards!

description.en: G2 is a concise and progressive visualization grammar for dashboard building, data exploration and storytelling.
Any chart can be drawn flexibly based on graphic syntax to satisfy your unlimited creativity
On top of a large number of product practices, it provides a drawing engine, a complete graphics grammar, and professional design rules
owerful interactive syntax to help visual analysis and make charts come alive
Real data visualization cases, we summarize them into story-based design templates, allowing users to achieve out-of-the-box effects.
